<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>soulfire is indeed a very good sword BUT you are all wrong, i was level 45 when i did MY testimony quest heheh you dont have to get the quest just give him the stuff require and you get your testimony</font></td></tr></table>
